+### 2.5 â€” `mfs.smali`: 5 Exynos-Focused Patches
+
+**File:** `smali_classes2/mfs.smali` Â· **Class:** `Lmfs;` Â· **Dex:** `classes2.dex`
+
+**Role:** Main HDR+/GCam processing pipeline â€” core algorithm for AWB, tone mapping, HDR merging, frame metadata.
+
+#### Patch 2.5.1 â€” AWB Processing Exynos Bypass (line ~3476)
+
+```diff
++     invoke-static {}, Lsgcam/default/DeviceCodeNames;->IdentifyExynos()Z
++     move-result v9
++     if-nez v9, :cond_2
+      if-nez v8, :cond_2
+```
+
+**Logic:** Original: if `AwbGainSelections() == 0` â†’ fill AWB gains with 1.0. New: if `IdentifyExynos() == true` â†’ also skip the fill block, deferring to `Shamim.GetAwbGain()`. Uses register `v9`.
+
+#### Patch 2.5.2 â€” ColorSpaceTransform Null on Exynos (line ~3556)
+
+```diff
++     invoke-static {}, Lsgcam/default/DeviceCodeNames;->IdentifyExynos()Z
++     move-result v8
++     if-eqz v8, :cond_exynos_ct
++     const/4 p1, 0x0
++     :cond_exynos_ct
+      check-cast p1, Landroid/hardware/camera2/params/ColorSpaceTransform;
+```
+
+**Logic:** On Exynos, nulls `ColorSpaceTransform`. Downstream handles null gracefully (uses fallback). Fixes color shifts/crashes from incompatible Exynos color transforms.
+
+#### Patch 2.5.3 â€” const/16 â†’ const/4 Optimization (line ~3703)
+
+```diff
+-    const/16 v16, 0x0
++    const/4 v16, 0x0
+```
+
+Cosmetic. `const/4` = 2 bytes vs `const/16` = 3 bytes. Same value `0`. No functional change.
+
