+## 5. KernelSU Module Design Considerations
+
+### 5.1 â€” Patching Strategy Options
+
+| Strategy | Complexity | Reliability | Persistence |
+|---|---|---|---|
+| **Boot-time DEX patch** | High | Medium | Per-boot |
+| **APK repack + replace** | Medium | High | Permanent |
+| **Module.prop + post-fs-data.sh overlay** | Low | Medium | Per-boot |
+| **Runtime hook (LD_PRELOAD/Xposed)** | Very High | Low | Per-boot |
+
+### 5.2 â€” Exynos-Specific vs Universal
+
+| Patch | Exynos Only? | Reason |
+|---|---|---|
+| `asw â€” acquireLatestImage` | No | Universal performance fix |
+| `dwn â€” Medium resolution` | No | Universal preference |
+| `dws â€” RawProcessing thread` | No | Universal bug fix |
+| `asz â€” comment` | N/A | No functional change |
+| `mfs â€” AWB bypass` | **Yes** | Checks `IdentifyExynos()` |
+| `mfs â€” ColorTransform null` | **Yes** | Checks `IdentifyExynos()` |
+| `mfs â€” const/4` | No | Cosmetic |
+| `mfs â€” HNU debug` | No | Debug logging |
+| `Pref â€” caching` | No | Universal performance fix |
+| `Shamim â€” AWB logging removed` | No | Cleanup |
+| `Shamim â€” GetAwbGain()` | **Yes** | Checks `IdentifyExynos()` |
+| `Shamim â€” GetBlackLevel()` | **Yes** | Checks `IdentifyExynos()` |
+| `Shamim â€” GetDefaultString()` | No | Universal perf fix |
+| `Shamim â€” Preview lag fix` | No (critical for Exynos) | Fixes HAL defaults uniquely broken on Exynos |
+
+### 5.3 â€” Recommended Patch Order
+
+1. **`asz.smali`** â€” comment (optional)
+2. **`Pref.smali`** â€” caching refactor (adds new methods, needed by others)
